The paper discusses the architecture design for mission-oriented miniature fixed-wing UAV swarms, which involves topics related to robotics (cs.RO), control systems (cs.SY), and machine learning (cs.MA, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper proposes a modular and distributed architecture, which can be relevant to software engineering (cs.SE). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.RO and cs.SY, followed by cs.MA, cs.AI, and cs.SE.
